      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>roasted</strong> <strong>peanuts </strong>to a baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 3-4 min or until toasted and lightly golden</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don’t burn!</p><p>Once toasted, remove from the oven and set aside</p>",
